resultSet.resultTitle: Don't reuse the same link text for links that have different destinations
resultSet.errorDescription: This link has the same text as another link that goes to a different place. Using the same text for multiple links which point to different pages is ambiguous and may be confusing for assistive technology users, or for users who have a cognitive disability.
